<subSubSection id="D08B3BFBCF8DA33E9BD86BF13A54FA75" pageId="0" pageNumber="107" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="516892C3429E19520AC411AF8C81FC37" pageId="0" pageNumber="107">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6ADC38CA8AFDA294AF133BB6DB4EBA09" pageId="0" pageNumber="107">The species name, to be treated as a noun in apposition, refers to the Maya people whose culture has been dominant in this region for more than 1000 years.</paragraph>
